Viernes, Julio 21, 2017







Image via Getty  Michael Loccisano
Chester Bennington could flat-out wail.US talk show host Jimmy Kimmel, 49, also took to the social networking platform to share a touching message about the star, saying: "Chester was one of the kindest men I've had on my show". Thoughts of you flooded my mind and I wept.
